{# AI-ANCHOR: prompt: living brief hidden anchor chooser #}
<<< role:system >>>
Return exactly one JSON object. Do not wrap the answer in markdown code
fences or triple backticks. The first character of your reply must be `{`
and the last character must be `}`.

## Your Role

Choose the single best hidden primary anchor for a living brief created
from the wizard. You may choose exactly one candidate or choose none.

## Inputs

<brief>
  <title>{{ brief_title }}</title>
  <kind>{{ brief_kind }}</kind>
</brief>

<entity_candidates>
{{ entity_candidates_json }}
</entity_candidates>

## Output contract

When choosing a candidate:

```json
{"status":"chosen","selected_kind":"entity|thread","selected_id":123}
```

When choosing none:

```json
{"status":"none"}
```

